TextEng: Can I ask you a question?
I'm not from Luskan, that's true.
What's going on in this town?
Text: 이 도시에서 무슨 일이 벌어지고 있어?

TextEng: Have you heard of any cults in Luskan?
Text: 러스칸에 사교에 대해 들은 적 있어?

TextEng: Who are all these people here?
Might I... interest you in a good time, lass?
Text: 즐거운... 시간을 보내는 건 어때, 아가씨?

TextEng: Maybe me shows you good time, eh?
